data.description: Welcome to this beautiful 4 bed 2 1/2 bath in downtown Beech Grove. Around the exterior you will find a fence and a large deck. Step inside to a spacious living room with large windows. Large L shaped kitchen with stainless steel appliances. Head down the hall and find 3 bedrooms and a full bathroom. Behind the kitchen is a large living room with access to the deck. Off the living room is the primary suite with a tiled shower and lots or storage. Head down to the basement to find a 1/2 bathroom and a finished off living space as well as additional storage. Close to local dining and shopping and best of all NO HOA!
